Kinetic Design
Maximize your performance marketing results without compromising your brand.  










Strike the perfect balance of brand-inspired design and unmatched ad performance.
At Criteo, we continually drive more engagement, more conversions and more ROI through industry-leading performance marketing. And we do this while keeping your brand consistent and visually appealing.
Criteo Dynamic Retargeting with Kinetic Design engages each shopper with creative optimized for that individual, device and channel driving 15% more revenue compared to static ads.
This flexible, patent-pending technology gives you real-time access to all available and relevant inventory in Criteo’s vast publisher network, free from design restrictions like size or layout. Simply put, you control your message and brand experience across the broadest range of digital inventory — and maximize your sales.







Kinetic Design offers you:





A dedicated creative services team
Our collaborative team of highly experienced design professionals creates your brand-led design foundation quickly and efficiently, and then continuously monitors and optimizes your campaigns.



Unmatched reach & flexibility
Our unique, automated ad-building technology ensures that your ads display perfectly in any layout or size. As new formats and placement opportunities arise, your ads are always ready to go — with zero delay.



Unparalleled personalized engagement
We tailor the components and layout of every ad to match the display context and specific phase of that particular consumer’s buying journey — in real-time










						How it works
					





Consistent Brand Framework Our experienced designers use your brand guidelines to establish a framework that will be carried throughout your campaigns.
Flexible, Digital Building BlocksYour essential design elements are broken down into a pool of ready-to-use digital components.
Personalized CustomizationFor each ad that is served, our technology automatically selects the optimal components for that specific consumer and context (browsing behavior, purchase intent, design preferences, type of device, etc.).
Perfect, Real-Time AlignmentThe ads are then rendered on the page in real-time, precisely meeting the size requirements for that publisher. 








Trillions of Creative Options Based on Real Data
Kinetic Design combines the best of human creativity with unparalleled data on consumer behavior and intent.




